Halin da ake ciki na kamuwa da cutar korona (COVID-19) a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin halin da kasashen Tarayyar Turai/Abokan Cinikayya da Burtaniya ke ciki, wanda ke nuna cewa, duk da cewa annobar COVID-19 tana da matakai daban-daban a kasashe daban-daban, tana karuwa a cikin sauri a duk duniya.
Dangane da yanayin Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci da dakunan jinya masu matukar wahala dole ne su kara kasancewa cikin shiri saboda karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman kulawa mai mahimmanci.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an gano wasu marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar huhu a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa cutar ta samo asali ne daga kwayar cutar coronavirus da ba a san asalinsa ba, wanda yanzu aka sani da cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Binciken ya nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke dauke da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, wato, kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da kumburi ba, kuma mafi yawan sun warke.
A kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari na yankuna, COVID-19 ya zama babban cuta da ke buƙatar asibiti kuma kashi 6 cikin ɗari na mutane suna da mummunan cuta da ke buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci.
Kasuwancin COVID-19 da suka mutu sun kai kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika karuwar cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Turai (UK) kuma mun kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK da Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Al'ummar EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun kamu da cutar COVID-19
Bayan kasar Sin, COVID-19 ya bazu zuwa wasu yankuna kuma yanayin barkewar COVID-19 a wasu sassan duniya ya bi na kasar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris na shekarar 2020, Babban Jami'in Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
A cikin wani rahoto na Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5 ga watan Agusta, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun bayyana farkon cutar COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A EU/EEA, an gano cutar ta farko a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga watan Maris na 2020, an riga an gano cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya, wanda a cikin wannan tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, akwai masu kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da kamuwa da cutar 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da kuma mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a matsayin ci gaba
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ta bayyana adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kowace kasa a duniya, daga cibiyoyin sadarwa na kasa da kasa, kamar ma'aikatar lafiya, da kuma cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya na WHO, da kuma cibiyoyin sadarwa, ana sabunta su a kowace rana da karfe 2:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanin don nazarin yanayin COVID-19 a EU/EEA da Burtaniya, kuma an kwatanta shi da na Italiya.
A matsayin tsarin kididdigar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da ke kan magani, mun lissafa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 da aka gano a cikin kwanaki 14, a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a kowace kasa kamar yadda ya karu a ranar 15 ga watan Agusta 2020 da karfe 2:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a lokacin 31 ga watan Janairu zuwa 15 ga watan Maris.
Halin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Matsakaicin adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 da aka samu a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya sun bi na lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya gabaɗaya, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Litinin).
Wannan ya kasance saboda saurin karuwar adadin daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun sami karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 (Hotspot).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga watan Maris da karfe 2:00 na safe, sauran kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya suna da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da ya yi daidai da na Italiya a makonni 3 da suka gabata ko kasa da haka.
Bayananmu sun nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 na karuwa sosai a EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
