A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana cewa kashi 10% na masu fama da cutar COVID-19 suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma labarai sun nuna cewa asibitoci da dakunan kulawa mai tsanani a yankunan sun cika.
Adadin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke kwance a asibiti da / ko ɗakunan kulawa mai mahimmanci waɗanda aka ƙayyade a matakin EU / EEA sun kai kashi 6% da 1%, (ba a ba da wannan bayanin ba).
Maimakon haka, dole ne a tattara su a cikin tsari mai kyau wanda ya dace da bayanan da aka nuna game da adadin masu cutar da mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a 2010/11 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin asibitocin gaggawa da asibitocin da ke kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, inda Jamus ke da asibitoci 29.2 da kuma Portugal tana da asibitoci 4.2 ga kowane mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa akwai ƙasashe da ke da mafi ko ƙasa da Italiya (kwakwalwa 12.5 na asibiti na gaggawa da kuma asibiti na kwantar da hankali ga mutane 100,000 a 2010).
Sakamakon da za a iya samu dangane da wadatar kayayyakin kiwon lafiya, bisa la'akari da adadin marasa lafiya da ke kwance da cutar COVID-19 a kowace kasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma matsalar da ake fuskanta idan bukatar asibitocin gaggawa ta wuce kashi 90%, an nuna a cikin rahoton ECDC na shida na saurin kimanta hadarin COVID-19.
Tun da yake har yanzu akwai wasu cututtuka a wasu ƙasashe na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da dakunan jinya na gaggawa suna ba da sabis ga mutanen da ke cikin yankuna da aka sani, za a samu bayanai game da marasa lafiya da kuma dakunan jinya a cikin tsarin Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Abubuwan da ke faruwa a Italiya da sauran ƙasashe sun nuna cewa rikicin COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, asibitoci da dakunan kula da gaggawa dole ne su kasance cikin shiri don yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'ummomin yankin da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, zuwa matakin da aka samu a yankunan Italiya da abin ya shafa.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken ECDC na gaggawa, ingantaccen shiri na gaggawa yana da mahimmanci wajen hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, duk da sauyawa daga hana yaduwa zuwa warkarwa, saboda karuwar gaggawa a cikin adadin masu cutar da ake tsammani a cikin iko ba zai ba hukumomi da asibitoci damar samun isasshen lokaci don fahimta, yarda da aiwatar da matakan tsaro idan ba a aiwatar da su ba da wuri.
Binciken da aka yi a baya ya nuna hanyoyin kiwon lafiya da za a bi don magance matsalar.
Akwai wasu kasafai da kasa ke da damar da za ta iya kara karfinta wajen rage yaduwar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma rage matsin lamba kan harkokin kiwon lafiya.
Idan wannan bai yi nasara ba, ana sa ran cewa za a sami matsalar kiwon lafiya a wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA saboda yawan marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ke haifar da cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma sama da mutane 80,000 sun kamu da cutar a China da sauran ƙasashe, wanda ya haifar da bala'in bala'i.
Kamar yadda cutar SARS-CoV, wadda ta haifar da cutar SARS a dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa ta hanyar huhu kuma yana haifar da alamun cutar.
A gefe guda, COVID-19 ba shi da ƙarfi kamar SARS kuma yana kashe mutane kaɗan amma yana da yaduwar yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi da maza fiye da matasa da mata.
Domin a amsa tambayoyin da aka yi game da wannan sabon ciwo, wannan talifin ya yi niyyar nuna cikakken bincike na wannan sabon ciwo.
Za mu tattauna abubuwa na asali game da cuta, abin da ke haddasa ta, ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewa, magani, hasashen nan gaba, da kuma guje wa su.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fatan wannan bincike zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma magance wannan cuta da ke damun mutane.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga Sinawa waɗanda aka nemi su zauna a gidajensu a duk lokacin hutu da makonni masu zuwa saboda barkewar cutar da kwayar cutar ba a san ta ba.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) da ta haifar da cutar sankarar numfashi (SARS) a 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya sunan SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu 2020, kuma an sake sanya sunan cutar da ke haifar da cutar CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma nan da nan ta bazu zuwa kasar da kuma wasu kasashe 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga watan Maris, 2020, cutar ta riga ta haifar da mutane sama da 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, sama da 40,000 sun warke kuma sama da 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine abokin gaba na mutum na 1 kuma yana iya zama mai haɗari fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin kasa da watanni biyu, an buga takardu sama da 200 kan COVID-19 wanda ya hada da bayanai game da kwayar cutar, cuta, sanadin cutar, bincike da magani tun daga rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 wanda ya gano kwayar cutar da aka ware daga marasa lafiya daban-daban.
Wannan binciken na nufin ci gaba da bincike a wannan sabon filin wasa mai saurin gudu.
A cikin wannan labarin, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wani cutar da ke haifar da CoV, cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda ya ɓarke a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abubuwan da muka koya game da yadda za mu guji wannan cuta da kuma wasu ra'ayoyi da kuma tambayoyi masu muhimmanci da ba a amsa ba.
CoVs an ɗauka cewa sun fi cutar mutum rauni, suna haifar da kashi 15% na kamuwa da cutar ta kowacce cuta 4.
A maimakon haka, a wannan karni, mun sami CoVs masu haɗari biyu ga ɗan adam, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka fara kamuwa da cutar a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe kuma suka kamu da cutar tare da kashe mutane da yawa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine CoV na uku da ya bayyana a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Hoto.Hoto.1,1, an fara bayar da rahoton cutar zazzabin cizon sauro a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta China.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an fitar da kwayar cutar CoV.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020 an bayar da rahoton kamuwa da cutar ta farko daga Wuhan.
A halin yanzu, cutar ta bazu cikin hanzari zuwa garuruwan da ke kewaye da ita, da kuma ƙasashe.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an sanar da cewa akwai wata cuta da ke sa mutane kamuwa da ita.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan kuma an dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairu, binciken farko na asibiti ya nuna cewa daga cikin mutane 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka kai hari kai tsaye a kasuwar kifi ta Wuhan, inda ake ganin cutar ta samo asali ne daga wani dabba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya.
A lokacin da ake rubuta wannan rahoto, cutar ta riga ta yaɗu a ƙasar Sin da kuma ƙasashe 50 a dukan duniya (Hoto (Hoto.2).2).
Yayin da yanayi ke canzawa, sakamakon da kuma girman matsalar har yanzu ba a sani ba.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, 2020, binciken da aka gudanar a wurare daban-daban kan mutane 8,866 da suka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya samar da sabon ma'anar cutar (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 na shafar mutane a duk shekaru, amma sama da shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne a ƙarƙashin shekaru 20, kuma marasa lafiya 14 ne kawai ke ƙasa da shekaru 10.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi yawa a cikin maza (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ya fi yawa a cikin al'umma fiye da yadda ya faru a Hubei da kewaye.
COVID-19 ya ɗauki kimanin kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga lokacin da ya fara zuwa lokacin da aka gano shi.
A lokacin da aka fara nuna alamun cutar, ya kai kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Lokaci daga lokacin da aka gano shi zuwa lokacin da ya mutu kwanaki 9.5 ne (4.8-13).
A cikin marasa lafiya, yawan haihuwa na asali (R0) ya kai 3.77 (CI 95%: 3.51-4.05), yayin da R0 da aka gyara ya kai 2.23-4.82.
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya yi tashin gwauron zabi kafin 23 ga watan Janairu, 2020, sakamakon yawan masu zirga-zirga kafin bikin bazara na kasar Sin.
