Kwayar cutar corona (CoVs) tana cikin kwayar cutar Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi nau'ikan ƙwayoyin cuta masu ƙyalli, kowane positive-sensed, kuma yana da RNA guda ɗaya.
An sanya sunayen kwayar cutar CoVs saboda irin nau'in da take kama da kambi da aka gano a cikin yisti.
A cikin masana'antu, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halitta da ba a cire su ba kuma suna tare.
Kusan kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta suna ɗauke da manyan abubuwa biyu masu kama da juna (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda suke haifar da pp1a da pp1ab.
Bayan haka, sai aka yi amfani da sunadarai masu yawa don a yi wasu sunadarai 16 da ake kira nsp1~16.
Sauran bangaren kwayoyin halitta suna dauke da ORFs a kan sunadarai masu tsari, wadanda suka hada da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Yawancin sunadarai masu amfani da layin halitta (lineage-specific accessory proteins) suna cikin jerin nau'ikan CoVs.
Bisa ga bambancin tsarin sunadarai, an rarraba CoVs zuwa manyan nau'ikan guda hudu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), wanda a cikinsu beta-CoV ne ke da mafi yawan kwayar cutar HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa layi huɗu (A, B, C da D).
