A cewar fitowar ta bakwai (3 ga watan Maris 2020), tabbatar da wanda ake zargi da cutar na bukatar hada daya daga cikin bayanan bayanan asibiti da kuma bayanan asibiti guda biyu domin yanke hukunci na karshe, ko kuma ya zama dole a kammala bayanan asibiti guda uku idan babu bayanan bayanan asibiti da aka sani:
Tarihin rashin lafiya: (1) kasancewar mutum a Wuhan da kewaye, ko kuma wasu yankuna da aka gano cewa akwai masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) kasancewar mutum yana tare da mutanen da ke dauke da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (ta hanyar gwajin nucleic acid mai kyau); (3) kasancewar mutum yana tare da masu cutar zazzabin cizon sauro ko masu fama da matsalar numfashi daga Wuhan da ke kewaye, ko kuma wasu yankuna da aka gano cewa akwai masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) kasancewar mutum yana tare da masu cutar (ƙananan masu cutar zazzabin cizon sauro ≥ 2 da kuma/ko kuma waɗanda ke da wahalar isa a cikin makonni 2 da suka gabata, kamar su gidajen abinci, ofisoshi, makarantu, da sauransu).
Alamun asibiti sune: (1) zazzabin cizon sauro da/ko wahalar numfashi; (2) alamun rashin lafiyar jiki da ke nuna cutar COVID-19; (3) yawan kwayoyin jini (white blood cells) da ke nuna ƙimar lymphocyte mai kyau, ko kuma raguwa a farkon lokacin.
Ya kamata a tabbatar da mai haƙuri idan akwai alamun cutar ko gwajin ruwa kamar yadda aka nuna a ƙasa: (1) idan gwajin PCR na gaggawa ya nuna cewa mutum yana da cutar SARS-CoV-2; (2) idan tsarin kwayar cutar kwayar cutar ya nuna kamannin da ke tattare da sabon kwayar cutar corona; (3) idan gwajin ruwa ya nuna cewa mutum yana da kwayar IgM da kwayar IgG ta SARS-CoV-2; ko kuma idan canjin kwayar cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 daga mara kyau zuwa mai kyau, ko kuma idan titer ya tashi sama da kwanaki ≥4 a lokacin warkewa fiye da lokacin da aka nuna rashin lafiya.
