Bangladesh ta sanar da karin mutane biyar da suka mutu sakamakon COVID-19, wanda shine mafi yawan mutuwar yau da kullun
Jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da cewa karin mutane biyar sun mutu sakamakon COVID-19 a wannan ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutane da suka mutu a rana daya saboda cutar.
Har zuwa jiya, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta yi rajistar mutane 114 da suka kamu da cutar kuma 33 sun warke a gida.
Jimillar wadanda suka mutu ya kai 17.
A wani rahoto da aka fitar a yanar gizo, jami'in IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ya ce wadanda suka mutu sun hada da maza hudu da mace daya.
A cewar Dr Meerjady, mutane biyu da suka mutu sun haura shekaru 60, biyu daga cikinsu suna tsakanin shekaru 51 zuwa 60, kuma daya daga cikinsu yana tsakanin shekaru 41 zuwa 50.
