An gano wadanda suka kamu da cutar ne a kasuwar sayar da abincin teku ta Huanan, inda ake ganin cutar ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi zuwa mutane.
Kwayar cutar da ta haifar da barkewar cutar ta SARS-CoV-2, sabuwar kwayar cutar da aka gano wacce ta yi kama da kwayar cutar bat coronaviruses, pangolin coronaviruses, da SARS-CoV. An gano mutum na farko da ya kamu da cutar a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma ba a gano cewa mutumin yana da alaƙa da sayar da kayan masarufi ba.
Daga cikin wadanda aka fara samun rahoto a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku na wadanda aka samu sun yi nasaba da wannan kasuwar.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris na shekarar 2020, wani rahoto da ba a bayyana ba daga South China Morning Post ya nuna cewa wanda ya kamu da cutar a ranar 17 ga watan Nuwamba na shekarar 2019, mai shekaru 55 daga lardin Hubei, na iya zama wanda ya fara kamuwa da cutar. A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairun 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa yayin da sabbin cututtuka suka ragu a China amma suka karu da sauri a Italiya, Iran, da Koriya ta Kudu, adadin sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar a wajen kasar Sin ya zarce sabon masu kamuwa da cutar a cikin kasar Sin a karon farko.
Wataƙila akwai wasu ƙididdigar marasa lafiya da ba a bayyana ba musamman waɗanda ba su da alamun cutar.
A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu karamin adadin mutane da suka kamu da cutar a tsakanin matasa masu shekaru 19 zuwa kasa da suka kai kashi 2.4% na wadanda suka kamu da cutar a duniya. Babban mai ba da shawara kan harkokin kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60% na yawan jama'ar Burtaniya na iya kamuwa da cutar kafin a samu kamuwa da cutar a cikin mutane.
