Wadannan sun danganta ne da kasuwar kifin Huanan (Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market), wanda ke sayar da dabbobi masu rai, kuma wani ra'ayi ya ce kwayar cutar ta samo asali ne daga daya daga cikin wadannan dabbobi; ko, a wasu kalmomin, asalinsa yana cikin dabbobi. An gano wani nau'in cutar huhu da ba a sani ba a ranar 26 ga Disamba wanda likita Zhang Jixian ya kula da shi a Asibitin lardin Hubei, wanda Wuhan Jianghan CDC ta ruwaito a ranar 27 ga Disamba.
