Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yaba wa kokarin da kasar Sin ke yi na shawo kan cutar.
WHO ta gano bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS a shekara ta 2002-2004, lokacin da aka bukaci shugabannin kasar Sin su yi shiru kan abin da ya hana hana a hana a hana a yi maganin cutar, da kuma halin da ake ciki yanzu da gwamnatin tsakiya "ke ci gaba da gargadi ga jama'a kan yadda za su guji yin zanga-zanga a shirye-shiryen bikin sabuwar shekara".
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a mayar da martani ga matakin da jami'an gwamnati suka dauka na dakatar da zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya ce, "duk da cewa ba WHO ce ta yanke shawarar ba, wannan mataki ne mai kyau da kuma nuna jajircewa wajen yaki da cutar a yankin da ta fi yaduwa" kuma ya bayyana shi a matsayin "wanda ba a taba ganin irinsa ba a tarihin kiwon lafiya". A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, lokacin da aka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum a wajen kasar Sin kuma yayin da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ke karuwa a kasashen waje, WHO ta ayyana cutar a matsayin Matsalar Lafiya ta Duniya (PHEIC), wanda ya zama na shida da aka bayyana a matsayin gaggawa tun lokacin da cutar ta barke a watan Oktoba na shekarar 2009.
Daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce PHEIC ta samo asali ne daga "matsalar yaduwar cutar a duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu karancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi waɗanda ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Da yake mayar da martani game da dakatar da sufuri, Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili da zai sa ba za a iya hana sufuri da cinikayya a duniya ba" kuma "WHO ba ta goyon bayan rage cinikayya da tafiye-tafiye ba".
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bukaci mutane a dukan duniya su ba da dala miliyan 675 don tallafa wa shirye-shirye a ƙasashe masu tasowa, ta nuna bukatar gaggawa na tallafa wa ƙasashe "waɗanda ba su da hanyoyin gano cutar idan ta ɓarke".
Tedros ya kuma bayyana cewa "ƙarfinmu ya yi daidai da inda muke da rauni" kuma ya yi kira ga mutane a duniya "su jira a yau ko kuma su biya mafi girma a nan gaba". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO a wani taron manema labarai ya sanar da COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya ce Sakataren Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da ba da "dukkanin ƙarfin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya don magance cututtuka".
An kafa tawagar kula da rikice-rikice ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya (UN Crisis Management Team), don daidaita ayyukan Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai taimaka musu "su mai da hankali kan kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomi ke ba da ƙwarewarsu don taimakawa al'amuran zamantakewa, tattalin arziki da ci gaba a lokacin annobar".
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, an kafa wata tawagar hadin gwiwa da WHO ta kafa a kasar Sin don isar da kwararru daga kasashen duniya da WHO zuwa kasar Sin don taimakawa wajen gudanar da ayyukan gida da kuma nazarin "matsanancin yaduwar cutar" ta hanyar shirya tarurruka da tarurruka tare da manyan hukumomi a cikin kasar da kuma tafiya zuwa yankuna don tabbatar da "sakamakon ayyukan da aka yi a matakin lardi da lardin, ciki har da yankunan birane da na karkara". A ranar 25 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta sanar da cewa "duniya ta fi shiri don yin la'akari da cewa cutar coronavirus na iya zama wata cuta ta duniya", kuma duk da cewa an riga an bayyana cutar a matsayin annoba ta duniya, kasashen sun ce ya kamata su kasance a shirye don "tsare kanta".
A ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a rage yawan cutar coronavirus a duniya daga "mai tsanani" zuwa "mai tsanani", wanda shine matakin da suka fi dacewa na kimantawa.
Mike Ryan, darektan shirin gaggawa na WHO, ya yi gargaɗi: "Wannan shi ne gwaji ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: Ku farka.
Cutar na iya kasancewa a kan hanya kuma kuna buƙatar kasancewa a shirye", ya yi gargadin cewa samun hanyoyin da suka dace na magance ta na iya taimaka wa duniya ta guji "mafi munin".
Ryan ya kuma ce bayanin da ake samu a yanzu bai sa jami'an kiwon lafiya su bayyana cutar a matsayin annoba ta duniya ba, ya ce irin wannan sanarwar zai nuna cewa "mun amince cewa kowa a duniya zai kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, WHO ta ayyana cutar coronavirus a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO na "da matukar damuwa game da yadda cutar ke yaduwa da kuma yadda take da muni, da kuma yadda ba a dauki mataki ba". WHO ta fuskanci zargi sosai saboda rashin iyawar da ta nuna wajen magance cutar, ciki har da jinkirin bayyana matsalar lafiya da gaggawa da kuma bayyana ta a matsayin babbar matsalar duniya.
Wannan zanga-zangar ta hada da neman daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom ya yi murabus, inda aka samu sa hannu 733,000 a ranar 6 ga watan Afrilu.
