Kwamitin ya ce kowa na da hakkin samun lafiya kuma wannan hakki ne na gwamnati.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin kayan aiki ko inshorar lafiya ba za a iya ɗauka a matsayin dalilin nuna wariya ga wasu mutane ba.
Masana sun nuna cewa kowa yana da hakkin samun lafiya, ciki har da nakasassu, 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, waɗanda ke cikin sansanonin 'yan gudun hijira, marasa gida, waɗanda ke cikin mawuyacin hali, fursunoni, da 'yan gudun hijira da duk wasu da ke bukatar taimakon gwamnati.
Hukumomin gwamnati a duk duniya suna magance tasirin COVID-19 ga tattalin arziki da zamantakewar al'umma.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwar tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kafa wata hanya ta hanyar bayar da cikakken bayani game da tsarin da aka kafa a kasashen duniya, da kuma ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
Daga dabarun inganta kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya zuwa magance tasirin kulle-kulle da rufe zirga-zirga, tsarin ya hada da Country Policy Tracker, wanda ke da nufin taimakawa kasashe su koyi darasi daga juna da kuma daidaita kokarin duniya wajen magance kalubalen coronavirus.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi wa Amurka, Ministan hukuma na Burtaniya Michael Gove, da kuma dan shugaban kasar Brazil Jair Bolsonaro Eduardo Bolsonaro korafi kan yadda suka magance matsalar, wadda ta fara ne a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An kori wasu manyan jami'an jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin (CPC) daga mukamin saboda yadda suka gudanar da aikin killace mutane a tsakiyar kasar Sin, wanda ke nuna rashin gamsuwa da yadda hukumomi ke kula da cutar a yankin.
Wasu masu sa ido sun yi imanin cewa an yi wannan ne don kare Sakataren Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin Xi Jinping daga fushin jama'a game da cutar coronavirus.
