Wannan bambancin zai iya shafar yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya, wanda zai iya zama mafi girma a wasu ƙasashe.
Ta amfani da tsarin sake fasalin polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) na lokaci na ainihi, ana iya yin gwajin ne a kan samfurori na jini da aka samo ta hanyoyi daban-daban, ciki har da hanci da hanci da kuma fitsari ko kuma samfurin da aka gano.
Ana samun sakamako a cikin 'yan sa'o'i zuwa kwanaki 2.
Ana iya yin gwajin RT-PCR da kuma gwajin kwayar cutar a cikin mako na farko na kamuwa da cutar.
Bayan haka, ƙwayoyin cuta za su iya ɓace a cikin hanci yayin da suke ƙara yawaita a cikin huhu.
Ga marasa lafiya da aka gwada a mako na biyu, ana iya cire samfurori daga cikin jijiyoyin numfashi ta hanyar amfani da catheter na tsotsa ko kuma ana iya amfani da mai bincike.
An fara yin gwajin PCR a Charité a Berlin a watan Fabrairun 2020 ta hanyar yin amfani da kwafin polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), wanda ya haifar da kayan aikin gwaji 250,000 da aka ba wa Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO).
