ACE2 yana hana aikin enzyme mai canza angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage yawan angiotensin-II ta hanyar kara Ang ((1-7) don sanya shi magani mai amfani don cutar zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki azaman mai gabatar da rigakafi ga wasu coronavirus.
