Kwayar ACE2 tana da N-terminal peptidase M2 domain da kuma C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 yana wucewa ta hanyar fata sau ɗaya, tare da manyan abubuwan da ke cikinsa a kan farfajiyar farfajiyar da ke cikin hanta da sauran jijiyoyi.
Ana amfani da wani abu da ake kira sheddase wajen fitar da ACE2 daga cikin fata, kuma ana amfani da shi wajen fitar da ruwan da ke cikin jini kuma a sake shi zuwa ruwa.
ACE2 yana samuwa a yawancin sassan jiki: ACE2 yana ɗaure ga ƙwayoyin halitta musamman ma na ƙwayoyin cuta na II a kan ganuwar ƙwayoyin cuta, ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta, jijiyoyin jini da ƙwayoyin cuta, da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta na jijiyoyin jiki a yawancin sassan jiki.
