ACE yana ɗaure ga angiotensin I hormone a cikin vasoconstricting angiotensin II.
ACE2 kuma yana ɗaure zuwa carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ya bayyana a cikin mai haɓaka angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma na iya ɗaure kan sarƙoƙi da yawa da suka haɗa da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana sarrafa tafiyar da kwayar halitta ta amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 wanda ake zargi da cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai dauke da kwayar halitta, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babbar hanyar shiga rigakafin wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na corona, ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar COVID-19).
