A ƙasar Sin, adadin mutanen da suke mutuwa ya kai kashi 2.8 cikin ɗari na maza, da kuma kashi 1.7 cikin ɗari na mata.
Ba a san ainihin dalilin da ya sa ake da bambanci tsakanin mata da maza ba, amma za a iya ganin cewa hali da kuma kwayoyin halitta suna da tasiri.
Bambancin jinsi bisa ga yawan shan taba, mata masu shan taba da yawa da maza masu fama da cututtuka kamar su ciwon daji a cikin shekaru fiye da mata na iya haifar da yawan mutuwar maza.
A Turai, kashi 57% na masu kamuwa da cutar maza ne kuma kashi 72% na waɗanda suka mutu daga COVID-19 maza ne.
Har zuwa watan Afrilu 2020, gwamnatin Amurka ba ta bin diddigin bayanan jinsi a cikin masu cutar COVID-19 ba.
Bincike ya nuna cewa cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta kamar Ebola, HIV, mura da SARS suna shafar maza da mata daban.
Yawancin likitoci, musamman ma mata, sun fi saurin kamuwa da cutar.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar a ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairun 2020 cewa sunan hukumar na cutar zai zama "COVID-19".
Babban Daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ya bayyana cewa CO yana wakiltar corona, VI don kwayar cutar, D don cutar, da 19 lokacin da aka fara gano cutar: 31 ga Disamba, 2019.
An zaɓi sunan don kaucewa yin magana game da kowane wuri (misali China), nau'in dabbobi ko rukuni na mutane, bisa ga ƙa'idodin duniya don kauce wa nuna bambanci. An kira kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19 da cutar coronavirus 2 mai saurin numfashi (SARS-CoV-2).
WHO ta kuma yi amfani da "kwayar COVID-19" da "kwayar cutar da ke da alhakin COVID-19" a cikin sadarwa da jama'a.
Dukkanin su, ana kiran cutar ta "coronavirus".
A lokacin da aka fara gano cutar a Wuhan, China, an kira kwayar cutar da cutar "coronavirus" da "Wuhan coronavirus".
A watan Janairun 2020, WHO ta amince da cutar numfashi mai saurin 2019-nCov da 2019-nCoV a matsayin sunaye na lokaci don a kira su cutar da cutar bayan shawarwarin 2015 na hana amfani da wuraren watsawa na cututtuka da ƙwayoyin cuta.
An fitar da sunayen hukuma na COVID-19 da SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu 2020.
Saboda ƙarancin iyawar samar da kayayyaki na yau da kullun, wasu masana'antun suna samar da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya kamar su swabs na hanci da sassan kayan aikin numfashi.
Alal misali, sa'ad da asibiti a Italiya ya bukaci bawul na na'urar numfashi, amma ba a kawo shi a kan lokaci ba, wani kamfani a ƙasar ya soma ƙera bawul guda 100 a dare ɗaya.
Bayan barkewar cutar COVID-19, an fara samun jita-jita, labaran karya game da asalin cutar, girmanta, rigakafinta da maganin ta da kuma wasu bayanai game da cutar da suka bazu a duk fadin yanar gizo cikin kankanin lokaci.
Mutane suna iya yaɗa wannan cuta ga dabbobi.
Binciken bai sami bayanai game da kamuwa da kwayar cutar a aladu, aladu, da kaji ba.
Babu magani ko rigakafin cutar da aka tabbatar.
Binciken duniya kan allurar rigakafin COVID-19 ana gudanar da shi ta hanyar hukumomin gwamnati, kungiyoyin bincike, da masu binciken kwayar cutar.
A watan Maris, WHO ta kaddamar da wani tsari mai suna "TESTING IN AVAILA" don tantance ko maganin da ake da shi a yanzu ya fi inganci.
Babu maganin rigakafi amma hukumomi da dama suna kokarin gano wanda zai taimaka.
Ana amfani da binciken farko na SARS-CoV saboda SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 duk suna amfani da mai karɓar ACE2 don shiga cikin kwayar cutar mutum.
Akwai nau'o'in rigakafi guda uku da ake bincike a kansu.
Da farko, masu bincike suna ƙoƙari su yi maganin da zai kawar da cutar.
Yin amfani da kwayar cutar, ko tana raye ko a raye, yana nufin samar da rigakafin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19.
Wani zaɓi, allurar rigakafi mai suna subunit vaccines, wannan tsari yana nufin samar da rigakafi wanda zai sa kwayar cutar ta hana kamuwa da kwayar cutar.
A cikin SARS-CoV-2, binciken ya mai da hankali kan furotin S-spike wanda ke taimakawa kwayar cutar ta shiga cikin mai karɓar enzyme na ACE2.
Hanya ta uku ita ce rigakafin nucleic acid (DNA ko RNA vaccines, sabuwar hanyar samar da rigakafi).
Alluran rigakafin da aka gwada daga waɗannan hanyoyin za su buƙaci gwaji don tabbatar da amincin su da kuma ingantaccen magani. A ranar 16 ga Maris, 2020, an fara gwajin farko na asibiti tare da masu ba da gudummawa huɗu a Seattle.
Magungunan rigakafi sun ƙunshi kwayar halitta mara lahani da aka kwafa daga kwayar cutar. An bayyana cewa inganta tsarin garkuwar jiki na iya zama ƙalubale wajen samar da allurar rigakafin SARS-COV-2, amma wannan ba gaskiya bane.
Ya zuwa watan Afrilu na 2020, an gudanar da gwaje-gwaje na asibiti sama da 300.
Gwaje-gwaje bakwai sun bincika magungunan da aka riga aka amince da su don maganin zazzabin cizon sauro, ciki har da gwaje-gwaje huɗu na hydroxychloroquine ko chloroquine.
Magungunan rigakafin cutar da ake amfani da su wajen magance cututtuka na daban sun kasance babban ɓangare na binciken kasar Sin, tare da gwajin kashi na III na remdesivir tara a ƙasashe da dama yayin da aka fitar da rahotanni a ƙarshen Afrilu.
An fara gwajin gwaji na gwaji don samar da allurar rigakafin COVID-19 da kuma yiwuwar magani a watan Afrilu na 2020. Ana nazarin magungunan rigakafi da yawa don magance COVID-19, gami da, remdesivir, chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir da lopinavir/ritonavir tare da interferon beta.
A watan Maris na shekarar 2020, akwai wasu bayanai da ba a tabbatar da su ba cewa maganin remdesivir yana da amfani.
An samu karuwa a cikin marasa lafiya da ake yi wa maganin remdesivir mai amfani da tausayi.
Ana gudanar da gwajin gwaji na mataki na III a Amurka, China da Italiya. An gwada Chloroquine, wanda aka yi amfani da shi don maganin zazzabin cizon sauro, a China a watan Fabrairun 2020, tare da wasu sakamakon farko.
Maimakon haka, an nemi a yi nazari a kan batun.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya a Koriya da China sun goyi bayan amfani da chloroquine.
Amma, duk da cewa Cibiyar Kula da Kwayoyin cuta ta Wuhan, ta ba da shawarar shan kashi ɗaya a rana na gram ɗaya, ta yi gargadin cewa yawan shan wannan kashi yana da haɗari kuma yana iya kashe mutum.
A ranar 28 ga watan Maris na 2020, FDA ta ba da izinin gaggawa ta amince da amfani da hydroxychloroquine da chloroquine bisa shawarar likitoci da ke kula da marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Binciken ya nuna cewa ana bukatar karin allurai na ribavirin don hana SARS-CoV-2 a vitro.
An ba da shawarar yin nazarin Nitazoxanide a cikin kwayoyin halitta bayan da aka nuna rashin ƙarfi a cikin SARS-CoV-2. Sakamakon binciken ya nuna cewa farkon haɓakar furotin na farko na transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) yana da mahimmanci don shigar da SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar haɗuwa da mai karɓar ACE2.
Binciken chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine tare da ko ba tare da azithromycin ba suna da lahani da yawa waɗanda suka hana likitoci yarda da amfani da waɗannan magungunan ba tare da ƙarin bincike ba. Oseltamivir baya hana SARS-CoV-2 a cikin vitro kuma ba a san amfanin COVID-19 ba.
Cytokine storm na iya zama mummunan rauni yayin da COVID-19 ke yaduwa.
Akwai tabbacin cewa hydroxychloroquine na iya samun kaddarorin anti-cytokine storm. Tocilizumab an sanya shi cikin jerin da Hukumar Lafiya ta China ta yi bayan gudanar da bincike kadan.
Yana cikin matakin gwaji na matakin 2 na Italiya bayan gano alamun cutar a cikin mutane.
Yanzu an haɗa shi da gwajin jini na jini na serum ferritin don gano guguwar cytokine, kuma yana da niyyar kawar da irin wannan abu, wanda ake tsammanin zai kashe wasu marasa lafiya.
FDA ta amince da maganin mai karɓar mai karɓar Interleukin-6 bisa ga binciken da ya gabata don magance cutar cutar cytokine mai hana steroid ta hanyar wani abu, maganin CAR T cell a cikin 2017.
Ya zuwa yanzu, babu tabbaci mai ƙarfi cewa maganin maganin maganin CRS.
Ana ganin sauya tsarin rigakafin cutar da aka yi wa allurar rigakafin cutar ta hanyar yin amfani da maganin rigakafin cutar COVID-19 da aka yi wa mutanen da suka kamu da cutar.
An gwada wannan hanyar a kan SARS amma sakamakon bai zama na ƙarshe ba.
Anaesthesia wani magani ne wanda ke amfani da maganin rigakafi wanda ya shafi cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Sauran hanyoyin, kamar su maganin rigakafi da ke dogara da ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma/ko phagocytosis, suna yiwuwa.
Ana kuma ci gaba da yin amfani da wasu hanyoyin da za a iya amfani da su wajen magance cututtukan da ke hana yaduwar cuta, kamar su maganin rigakafi na monoclonal.
Za a iya ƙara maganin da ake kira convalescent serum, wanda ke ɗauke da jinin da aka yi amfani da shi a kan marasa lafiya da suka warke kuma yana ɗauke da ƙwayoyin cuta da ke hana kamuwa da cutar.
